{"tid":1509874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（眾籌）本地登報多謝戰場上同路人","createTime":"2019-08-27T03:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T13:42:31.000Z","uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1aff6a674e05619ec2ae135db66fce4c9f5b6c","tid":1509874,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"一直想多謝依場抗爭中既人，包含前線同後援，急救同記者<br />\n<br />\n前線和後援合作無間，成功阻止同揭發政府腐敗<br />\n<br />\n急救，在戰火紛飛情況下都留守保護每位人士情命，即是立場不同，亦不分善惡去盡責救人<br />\n<br />\n記者，無懼打壓，即使生命受威脅都力求報導事實真相<br />\n<br />\n相信好多人沒勇氣係戰場上同大家同行，但都想跟同路人表達自己謝意，希望可以眾籌係香港報紙，或網上落廣告，講大家知，抗爭者唔孤單，亦不是少數，你地做既野無錯。<br />\n<br />\n只要堅持民主自由信念，過去。現在，未來絕不割席！"},{"pid":"a18685e3c2ed98c5a4594acad77dcdf93cbe43ce","tid":1509874,"uid":103914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8EPwGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8EPwGM.png&h=cdc67ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=68430197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=0143543b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=f643b9fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pi